{"word":"G5425 - φρίσσω - phríssō - fris'-so - Tremble","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">φρίσσω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">phríssō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">fris'-so</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Tremble</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - நடுங்கு"},{"paragraph":"1. to bristle, stiffen, stand up: to be rough"},{"paragraph":"2. to shudder, to be struck with extreme fear, to be horrified"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Apparently a primary verb; to &ldquo;bristle&rdquo; or <i>chill</i>, that is, <i>shudder</i> (fear): - tremble.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}